案例，但该网站表示美国政府亦给当地的翻译人员设置了苛刻的避难申请条件，要求他们必须给美军服务超过2年才可以。 美国《纽约时报》和卡塔尔半岛电视台也在今年6月报道了这一给美国及其盟友军队充当翻译的阿富汗人所面临的困境。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+JSThLyIuLdkEAMaCDY3MDgyMzkyIPjmq4cGMGw4mA1AAXIJNDcxNjEyNzg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1363 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-23f7786d39411fa2e5fa0988d4e3f025_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1626080840.07833","card_id":"Q_471641951","target":{"id":471641951,"title":"电影《失孤》原型郭刚堂的儿子找到了，你有什么感想？防止儿童被拐卖，我们还能做哪些？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/471641951","type":"question","created":1626019483,"answer_count":350,"follower_count":1242,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,1395,2265,8326,188766],"comment_count":47,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"7月11日，紧急呼叫 从电影《失孤》原型郭刚堂处证实，他已获知儿子郭振的下落。郭刚堂与儿子DNA比对成功，警方已着手安排父子认亲事宜。1997年，2岁多的郭振被人贩拐卖。二十多年来，郭刚堂为寻找儿子，骑行40万多公里，跑了31个省，报废10辆摩托车。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+JSThLyIuLdkEAMaCDY3MDg4ODc4IJutrIcGMC842glAAnIJNDcxNjQxOTUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"972 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c1b308ccccb05c167d15c8941e7936fb_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1626080840.0788956","card_id":"Q_471268212","target":{"id":471268212,"title":"如何看待上海财经大学一女博士拿不到学位，学院称「论文不符要求」？是否与此前多次举报教授论文抄袭有关？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/471268212","type":"question","created":1625858146,"answer_count":132,"follower_count":908,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5259,7416,17088,125630,726204],"comment_count":17,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"吴莫萱（化名）被撤销博士学位的理由充分吗？跟她近年多次举报学院教授徐国祥的著作、论文涉嫌抄袭有关吗？双一流大学女博士拿不到学位，校方：其发表的论文不在规定期刊之列"},"att